Figure 3 compares the DC bias dependence of the measured EQE and ΔEQE with the calculated results. The calculated results, indicated by the solid lines, reproduce well the measured data. Here, we used the fitting parameters listed in Table 1, and the evaluated variations of τr and τesc are shown by the solid and dashed lines in Fig. 5. τr was calculated by using the empirical relation τr=τ0(1+Cr×F)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
